<subSubSection pageId="4" pageNumber="123" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="4.[151,756,720,809]" lastBlockId="4.[831,1437,258,577]" pageId="4" pageNumber="123">
<bibRefCitation author="Jeannel R." box="[151,454,720,745]" editor="Deboutteville C. D." journalOrPublisher="Centre National de la Recherche Scientifique, Paris" pageId="4" pageNumber="123" pagination="295 - 479" refString="Jeannel R. 1962. Les Pselaphides de la Paleantarctide Occidentale (pp. 295 - 479). In: Deboutteville C. D., Rapoport E. (eds), Biologie de l'Amerique Australe. Vol. I. Etude sur la Faune du Sol. Centre National de la Recherche Scientifique, Paris." title="Les Pselaphides de la Paleantarctide Occidentale" type="book chapter" volumeTitle="Biologie de l'Amerique Australe. Vol. I. Etude sur la Faune du Sol" year="1962">Jeannel (1962: 398, 402)</bibRefCitation>
characterized this group as follows: elytra with 2 basal foveae; basal striae of abdominal tergite I separated by 1/3 of tergal width; head with broad transverse occipital hump in male; frons not narrowed anteriorly in female; male antennomere X not enlarged; copulatory pieces of aedeagus thin.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="4.[831,1437,258,577]" pageId="4" pageNumber="123">
The group currently includes 
<taxonomicName authority="(Reitter, 1885)" authorityName="Reitter" authorityYear="1885" baseAuthorityName="Reitter" baseAuthorityYear="1885" box="[1155,1432,388,412]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Achilia" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="123" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="larvata">
<emphasis box="[1155,1263,388,412]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="123">A. larvata</emphasis>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Reitter E." box="[1279,1424,388,411]" journalOrPublisher="Deutsche Entomologische Zeitschrift" pageId="4" pageNumber="123" pagination="321 - 332" part="29" refString="Reitter E. 1885. Beitrag zur Kenntniss der Pselaphiden-Fauna von Valdivia, Zweiter Theil. Deutsche Entomologische Zeitschrift 29: 321 - 332, pl. II." title="Beitrag zur Kenntniss der Pselaphiden-Fauna von Valdivia, Zweiter Theil" type="journal article" year="1885">Reitter, 1885</bibRefCitation>
)
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName authority="Jeannel, 1962" authorityName="Jeannel" authorityYear="1962" box="[831,1170,420,444]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Achilia" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="123" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="tumidifrons">
<emphasis box="[831,993,420,444]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="123">A. tumidifrons</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Jeannel R." box="[1010,1170,421,444]" editor="Deboutteville C. D." journalOrPublisher="Centre National de la Recherche Scientifique, Paris" pageId="4" pageNumber="123" pagination="295 - 479" refString="Jeannel R. 1962. Les Pselaphides de la Paleantarctide Occidentale (pp. 295 - 479). In: Deboutteville C. D., Rapoport E. (eds), Biologie de l'Amerique Australe. Vol. I. Etude sur la Faune du Sol. Centre National de la Recherche Scientifique, Paris." title="Les Pselaphides de la Paleantarctide Occidentale" type="book chapter" volumeTitle="Biologie de l'Amerique Australe. Vol. I. Etude sur la Faune du Sol" year="1962">Jeannel, 1962</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName authority="Jeannel, 1962" authorityName="Jeannel" authorityYear="1962" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Achilia" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="123" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="globiceps">
<emphasis box="[1191,1207,421,444]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="123">A</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis box="[1230,1332,420,444]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="123">globiceps</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Jeannel R." editor="Deboutteville C. D." journalOrPublisher="Centre National de la Recherche Scientifique, Paris" pageId="4" pageNumber="123" pagination="295 - 479" refString="Jeannel R. 1962. Les Pselaphides de la Paleantarctide Occidentale (pp. 295 - 479). In: Deboutteville C. D., Rapoport E. (eds), Biologie de l'Amerique Australe. Vol. I. Etude sur la Faune du Sol. Centre National de la Recherche Scientifique, Paris." title="Les Pselaphides de la Paleantarctide Occidentale" type="book chapter" volumeTitle="Biologie de l'Amerique Australe. Vol. I. Etude sur la Faune du Sol" year="1962">Jeannel, 1962</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
, and 
<taxonomicName authority="Franz, 1996" authorityName="Franz" authorityYear="1996" box="[950,1279,453,478]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Achilia" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="123" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="paraglobiceps">
<emphasis box="[950,1135,453,477]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="123">A. paraglobiceps</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Franz H." box="[1145,1279,454,478]" journalOrPublisher="Koleopterologische Rundschau" pageId="4" pageNumber="123" pagination="83 - 146" part="66" refString="Franz H. 1996. Neue Beitrage zur Kenntnis der Pselaphidenfauna von Chile und Argentinien (Coleoptera: Pselaphidae). Koleopterologische Rundschau 66: 83 - 146." title="Neue Beitrage zur Kenntnis der Pselaphidenfauna von Chile und Argentinien (Coleoptera: Pselaphidae)" type="journal article" year="1996">Franz, 1996</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
. However, we place all of these names as 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Reitter" baseAuthorityYear="1885" box="[1155,1267,486,510]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Achilia" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="123" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="larvata">
<emphasis box="[1155,1267,486,510]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="123">A. larvata</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, becoming the only constitutive member in the unfortunately named 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Jeannel" authorityYear="1962" box="[831,953,551,575]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Achilia" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="123" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="tumidifrons">
<emphasis box="[831,953,551,575]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="123">tumidifrons</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
group.
</paragraph>
